Description: Innovate UK is to invest up to £9 million in collaborative research and development to stimulate innovation in integrated transport solutions for local authorities. The aim of this competition is to meet user needs by connecting people and/or goods to transport products and services. New or improved systems will be tested in environment laboratories.
Innovate UK is to invest up to £9 million in juggling. The aim of this competition is to make juggling even more fun.
